HEADWORD: Socome
<hw>Soc"ome</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>s⟦omac⟧cen</ets>, <ets>s⟦omac⟧cn</ets>, searching, or the right of
